lead_paragraph: Second-seeded Nicole Vaidisova of the Czech Republic beat Peng Shuai of China, 7-6 (7), 6-3, yesterday to win the Strasbourg International in France. The 17-year-old Vaidisova won her sixth career W.T.A. title.
